  Ti7 1448 ni5, I2-tai7-li7 kok khi2 kek-beng7, cheng3-hu2 kiaN5 liam-khau thiu peng e5 hoat-tou7, sia2 thong-siaN5 ta-pou-teng e5 mia5-siN3 ti7 kui7-lai7, chiau3 pah-hun7 liam kui2 e5, long2 u7 tiaN7-tioh8 e5 siau3-giah8. Chit8 e5 pu3 lang5 e5 kiaN2 chhau3-tu2-kham2 liam--tioh8, pe7-bu2 chin thiaN3--i, m7 kam hou7 i khi3, in-ui7 kiaN2 si7 Nng2-chiaN2 e5 thak8-chheh lang5, tng peng tioh8 tam hong tam hou7, poaN5-soaN ke3-nia2, kiaN-liau2 be7 kau3 chian3-tiuN5, i2-keng si2--khi3, tui3 an2-ni tiu5-tu5 boe7 koat-toan3. U7--e5 ka7 pu3-lang5 kong2, ¡§Li2 e5 kiaN2 khi3 tng-peng, sit8-chai7 ti7 chian3-su7 long2 bo5 li7-ek, put-ju5 chhut choe7-choe7 gun5, chhiaN2 iong2-kiaN7 u7 lat8 e5 lang5 lai5 thoe3, an2-ni pe7-bu2 bian2 hoan5-lo2, iu7 koh pi7-pan7 hap8 eng7 e5 jin5-chai5 pang-chan7 kok-ka, it ku2 liong2 tek, kiam2 bo5 khah ho2?¡¨ Pu3-lang5 chan3-seng5, chiu7 ti7 kok-lai7 si3-koe3 tah kong2-ko3, boe7 po3-choa2, kong2 na7 u7 lang5 u7 khui3-lat8, oe7 thoe3 goa2 e5 kiaN2 choe3 peng bo5 lun7 sim2-mih8 tiau5-kiaN7, iau-kiu5 sim2-mih8 mih8, hoan7-na7 goa2 e5 lat8 choe3 oe7 kau3--e5, long2 beh seng5-jin7, han7 bou2 geh8 bou2 jit8 lai5 chham-siong5. Kong2-ko3 chhut geh8-goa7 jit8 ku2, jip8 iaN5 e5 ki5 i2-keng kau3, long2 bo5 lang5 lai5 chiap-hiap8, pe7-bu2 toa7 iu-bun7, mi5-jit8 thi5-khau3. Chit8 jit8 chhe-iah8 lai5 tiau3 siau3-lian5 jip8 iaN5 po3 mia5, pe7-bu2, chi2-be7, chhin-chhek lai5 sang3 i kau3 siaN5-goa7, thi5-khau3 kau3 bo5 siaN. Hit si5 u7 chit8 e5 ke3-pak sio2-ti7 lai5 song3-heng5, chit-e5 bo5 pe7 bo5 bu2, tui3 soe3-han3 chiu7 hou7 chim2-chek chiau3-kou3 poe5-iong2. Ti7 lou7--nih8 hiaN-ti7 tam5-lun7 li7-piat8 e5 oe7, sio2-ti7 kong2, ¡§Goa2 kou-toaN chit8 sin, bo5 sou2 tiN5-poaN3, goan7 thoe3 li2 jip8 iaN5. Cheng5-jit8 in-ui7 kiaN chim2-chek m7 kheng2 chiah m7-kaN2 kong2, ho5-hong3 chim2-chek e5 un chin chhim ti7 goa2 tau, che chiaN3-si7 goa2 po3 un e5 si5. A-hiaN, lan2 e5 saN saN-oaN7 chheng7, hou7--goa2 teng2 li2 e5 mia5 khi3, koh goa2 e5 ni5-he3 bin7-mau7 kap li2 ch